{
"#name"
:
{
"bfind"
:
null
,
"cn"
:
"默认剪枝噪音目录的 BFS 封装，浅层优先，为 AI Agent 设计"
,
"en"
:
"BFS wrapper with default prune, shallow-first, for AI agents"
}
,
"#synopsis"
:
[
{
"x bfind [prune-args] [--depth N] [--] [path] [find-expr]"
:
null
}
,
{
"x bfind --dfs2bfs"
:
null
}
,
{
"x bfind ."
:
null
}
,
{
"x bfind --depth 5 ."
:
null
}
,
{
"x bfind --prune vendor -- . -type f"
:
null
}
]
,
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"与 x find 共享剪枝规则的广度优先搜索，浅层优先，适合逐步深入探索目录结构"
,
"en"
:
"Breadth-first search sharing prune rules with x find, shallow results first, ideal for incremental exploration"
}
,
"#tip"
:
[
{
"en"
:
"Shares the same three-dimension prune model as x find: (1) hidden dirs, (2) project noise, (3) HOME platform dirs. See x find --help for details.\n"
,
"cn"
:
"与 x find 共享三维剪枝模型：(1) 隐藏目录，(2) 项目噪音，(3) HOME 平台目录。详见 x find --help。\n"
}
,
{
"en"
:
"Default depth is 3. Use --depth to go deeper. For git projects, prefer git ls-files and git grep.\n"
,
"cn"
:
"默认搜索 3 层。用 --depth 加深。在 git 项目中优先使用 git ls-files 和 git grep。\n"
}
]
,
"--dfs2bfs"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"将 stdin 的 DFS 路径重排为 BFS 顺序输出"
,
"en"
:
"Reorder DFS paths from stdin into BFS order"
}
,
"#subcmd"
:
true
}
,
"--depth"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"设置最大深度（默认3）"
,
"en"
:
"Set maximum depth (default 3)"
}
,
"#1"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"深度值"
,
"en"
:
"Depth value"
}
}
}
,
"--unhide"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"放行指定隐藏目录（支持 : 分隔多值）"
,
"en"
:
"Exempt hidden dirs from prune (supports : separator)"
}
,
"#1"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"隐藏目录名（如 .vscode:.claude）"
,
"en"
:
"Hidden dir name (e.g. .vscode:.claude)"
}
}
}
,
"--prune"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"追加排除目录（支持 : 分隔多值）"
,
"en"
:
"Add prune targets (supports : separator)"
}
,
"#1"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"目录名（如 vendor:venv）"
,
"en"
:
"Dir name (e.g. vendor:venv)"
}
}
}
,
"--unhide-all"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"不排除任何隐藏目录"
,
"en"
:
"Do not exclude any hidden directories"
}
}
,
"--reset-prune"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"清空项目噪音列表（隐藏目录排除和 HOME 排除不受影响）"
,
"en"
:
"Clear project noise list (hidden dir prune and HOME prune unaffected)"
}
}
,
"--no-homeprune"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"关闭 $HOME 目录下的自动排除"
,
"en"
:
"Disable automatic HOME directory prune"
}
}
,
"--all"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"显示所有结果（不限制深度）"
,
"en"
:
"Show all results (unlimited depth)"
}
}
,
"-v|--verbose"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"显示当前生效的排除列表"
,
"en"
:
"Show active prune lists"
}
}
,
"#tldr"
:
[
{
"cmd"
:
"x bfind ."
,
"cn"
:
"BFS 搜索当前目录（默认3层）"
,
"en"
:
"BFS search current directory (default 3 layers)"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x bfind --depth 5 ."
,
"cn"
:
"5层搜索"
,
"en"
:
"5-layer search"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x bfind --all ."
,
"cn"
:
"显示全部结果"
,
"en"
:
"Show all results"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x bfind --prune vendor:target -- . -name \"*.go\""
,
"cn"
:
"排除 vendor 和 target，查找 .go 文件"
,
"en"
:
"Exclude vendor and target, find .go files"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x bfind --no-homeprune ~"
,
"cn"
:
"HOME 搜索，关闭 HOME 排除"
,
"en"
:
"HOME search, disable HOME prune"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x bfind --unhide-all --reset-prune --no-homeprune -- ."
,
"cn"
:
"三维全关，等同 raw find（BFS 模式）"
,
"en"
:
"All three dimensions off, raw find (BFS mode)"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"find . -name \"*.go\" | x bfind --dfs2bfs"
,
"cn"
:
"将 find 的 DFS 结果转为 BFS 顺序"
,
"en"
:
"Convert DFS find output to BFS order"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x find . -type f | x bfind --dfs2bfs"
,
"cn"
:
"将 x find 的结果按深度重排"
,
"en"
:
"Reorder x find results by depth"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"grep -rl \"TODO\" . | x bfind --dfs2bfs"
,
"cn"
:
"将 grep 匹配文件按浅层优先排列"
,
"en"
:
"List grep-matched files shallow-first"
}
]
}

